The library is written in C# and most of them support from .Net 2.0 to the latest .Net version.

FeedPackage.Description:
This package provides an example of how to use the type providers available in the FSharpx.TypeProviders library (using the TypedAppSettings type provider as an example). FSharpx.TypeProviders is a library for the .NET platform implementing common type providers on top of the FSharpx.Core. Its main target is F# but it aims to be compatible with all .NET languages wherever possible.
It currently implements type safe variants of:
* Regex * FileSystem * Csv * AppSettings.

FSharpx is a library for the .NET platform implementing general functional constructs on top of the F# core library. Its main target is F# but it aims to be compatible with all .NET languages wherever possible.
This library is for the .NET platform implementing a type provider for Xaml files.
